window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>After the pain of lost friends and party members, Tad, gold key in hand, faces the endless class tower. </b></p> <p>Mysteries and secrets lie within. Trials turn to battles with other voids. With new strength come new challenges. His warrior trial looms ahead, with warrior rank dungeons waiting beyond.&nbsp;</p> <p>Old friends and new band together to raid dungeons and find adventure in the second installment of the Dungeon Slayer LitRPG adventure series.</p>"; 
